Way off somewhere where Domnijoe and Blindchaos landed... the ground 
is now filled with alrge craters and where Domnijoes ship hand landed 
now lies a few craters with large chunks of unusable wreakage there.
(If someone builds a base from this stuff by using the "good Parts" I 
swear I will hurt you.) Vampiza hovers quietly in the air as he looks 
at the cratered terrain and sighs. Without a word said the big energy 
being is surrounded by Chaochitan energy once again and speeds off 
towards the Infecticon base, a course that would also make him pass 
over Alliance Island...
